<fieldset><legend><h2>
        <a href="/us/">Trending in the United States</a>
        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 11 Aug 2024 06:15:19 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 11 Aug 2024 06:15:19 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="RIO YAMAT, DARLENE SUPERVILLE, WILL WEISSERT and JOSH BOAK, Associated Press, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/11/in-las-vegas-kamala-harris-sees-a-chance-to-improve-her-odds-of-winning.webp" alt="Harris pledges to work to end taxes on tips for service industry employees, echoing Trump vow"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Harris pledges to work to end taxes on tips for service industry employees, echoing Trump vow</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      LAS VEGAS (AP) — Vice President Kamala Harris promised Saturday to work to eliminate taxes on tips paid to restaurant and other service industry employees, echoing a pledge that her opponent, Republican Donald Trump, has made, and marking a rare instance of political overlap from both sides.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/11/in-las-vegas-kamala-harris-sees-a-chance-to-improve-her-odds-of-winning/"  >(RIO YAMAT, DARLENE SUPERVILLE, WILL WEISSERT and JOSH BOAK, Associated Press, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 11 Aug 2024 02:01:45 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 11 Aug 2024 02:01:45 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="DAVID SHARP, MICHAEL HILL, MARK SCOLFORO and PATRICK WHITTLE, Associated Press, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/11/debby-finally-moves-out-of-the-us-though-risk-from-flooded-rivers-remains.webp" alt="Debby finally moves out of the US, though some flooding risk and power outages remain"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Debby finally moves out of the US, though some flooding risk and power outages remain</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The sun came out but the power stayed off in more than 100,000 homes and businesses across four states Saturday as Debby finally moved out of the U.S.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/11/debby-finally-moves-out-of-the-us-though-risk-from-flooded-rivers-remains/"  >(DAVID SHARP, MICHAEL HILL, MARK SCOLFORO and PATRICK WHITTLE, Associated Press, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 11 Aug 2024 21:15:47 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 11 Aug 2024 21:15:47 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="JAKE COYLE, Associated Press, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/11/who-won-at-the-box-office-this-weekend-the-reynolds-lively-household.webp" alt="Who won at the box office this weekend? The Reynolds-Lively household"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Who won at the box office this weekend? The Reynolds-Lively household</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Reynolds’ Marvel Studios smash “Deadpool &#038; Wolverine” remained the top movie in North American theaters for the third straight week, followed by “It Ends With Us,” the romance drama starring Lively, which surpassed expectations with a stellar $50 million debut.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/11/who-won-at-the-box-office-this-weekend-the-reynolds-lively-household/"  >(JAKE COYLE, Associated Press, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 12 Aug 2024 17:36:16 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 12 Aug 2024 17:36:16 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Addy Bink, KLAS, CBS News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/12/rare-severe-geomagnetic-storm-hits-earth-will-it-impact-the-grid.webp" alt="Rare, severe geomagnetic storm hits Earth: Will it impact the grid?"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Rare, severe geomagnetic storm hits Earth: Will it impact the grid?</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Geomagnetic storm conditions observed over the weekend strengthened Monday morning, creating a "major disturbance in Earth's magnetic field," the Space Weather Prediction Center said.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/12/rare-severe-geomagnetic-storm-hits-earth-will-it-impact-the-grid/"  >(Addy Bink, KLAS, CBS News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 12 Aug 2024 05:50:31 -0400">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 12 Aug 2024 05:50:31 -0400">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/12/illinois-school-worker-sentenced-9-years-prison-stealing-1-5-million-worth-chicken-wings.webp" alt="Illinois school worker sentenced to 9 years in prison for stealing $1.5 million worth of chicken wings"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Illinois school worker sentenced to 9 years in prison for stealing $1.5 million worth of chicken wings</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A former food service director for an Illinois school district was sentenced to nine years in prison for stealing $1.5 million worth of chicken wings meant for students.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/12/illinois-school-worker-sentenced-9-years-prison-stealing-1-5-million-worth-chicken-wings/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 11 Aug 2024 19:32:39 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 11 Aug 2024 19:32:39 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/11/us-ties-china-in-paris-olympics-gold-medal-count-after-americans-nail-biting-womens-hoops-win.webp" alt="US ties China in Paris Olympics gold medal count after Americans' nail-biting women's hoops win"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">US ties China in Paris Olympics gold medal count after Americans' nail-biting women's hoops win</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The U.S. women’s basketball team held off France to win gold in the final event of the Paris Olympics, and that hardware was needed for the Americans to tie China for the most with 40.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/11/us-ties-china-in-paris-olympics-gold-medal-count-after-americans-nail-biting-womens-hoops-win/"  >(The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 12 Aug 2024 20:12:03 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 12 Aug 2024 20:12:03 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="LOLITA C. BALDOR, Associated Press, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/12/pentagon-chief-orders-submarine-to-the-middle-east-tells-aircraft-carrier-to-hasten-its-transit.webp" alt="US beefs up posture in Middle East, warns an Iran-backed attack on Israel could come this week"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">US beefs up posture in Middle East, warns an Iran-backed attack on Israel could come this week</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      WASHINGTON (AP) — U.S. Defense Secretary Lloyd Austin has ordered a guided missile submarine to the Middle East and is telling the USS Abraham Lincoln aircraft carrier strike group to sail more quickly to the area, as the U.S.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/12/pentagon-chief-orders-submarine-to-the-middle-east-tells-aircraft-carrier-to-hasten-its-transit/"  >(LOLITA C. BALDOR, Associated Press, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
        <a href="/world/">Around the world</a>
        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 11 Aug 2024 19:33:25 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 11 Aug 2024 19:33:25 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Miranda Nazzaro, The Hill">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/11/biden-says-gaza-cease-fire-still-possible-working-literally-every-single-day-to-stop-escalation-of-war.webp" alt="Biden says&#160;Gaza&#160;cease-fire still possible, working 'literally every single day' to stop escalation of war"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Biden says&#160;Gaza&#160;cease-fire still possible, working 'literally every single day' to stop escalation of war</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      President Biden said he believes a cease-fire deal in the Israel-Hamas war is "still possible" before the end of his Oval Office term in just more than five months.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/11/biden-says-gaza-cease-fire-still-possible-working-literally-every-single-day-to-stop-escalation-of-war/"  >(Miranda Nazzaro, The Hill)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 12 Aug 2024 09:24:13 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 12 Aug 2024 09:24:13 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Samya Kullab, Associated Press, Local 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/12/more-russians-are-urged-to-flee-ukraines-cross-border-attack-as-the-kremlin-scrambles-to-respond.webp" alt="Top Ukrainian commander says his forces now control almost 390 square miles of Russia's Kursk region"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Top Ukrainian commander says his forces now control almost 390 square miles of Russia's Kursk region</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Ukraine’s top military commander says his forces now control 1,000 square kilometers, or 386 square miles, of Russia’s neighboring Kursk region.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/12/more-russians-are-urged-to-flee-ukraines-cross-border-attack-as-the-kremlin-scrambles-to-respond/"  >(Samya Kullab, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 12 Aug 2024 08:38:57 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 12 Aug 2024 08:38:57 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="MARI YAMAGUCHI, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/12/storm-dumps-intense-rainfall-on-northern-japan-sending-some-people-to-shelters.webp" alt="Storm dumps intense rainfall on northern Japan, sending some people to shelters"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Storm dumps intense rainfall on northern Japan, sending some people to shelters</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      TOKYO (AP) — A slow-moving storm has been dumping intense rains on northern Japan, swelling rivers, sending residents to shelters and disrupting traffic during a Japanese Buddhist holiday week. The storm was once Typhoon Maria but has weakened, with winds now blowing up to 72 kph (45 mph).
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/12/storm-dumps-intense-rainfall-on-northern-japan-sending-some-people-to-shelters/"  >(MARI YAMAGUCHI, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 09 Aug 2024 14:25:43 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 09 Aug 2024 14:25:43 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/09/what-to-watch-friday-breaking-boxing-and-more-track-and-field.webp" alt="What to watch Friday: Breaking, Boxing and more track and field"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">What to watch Friday: Breaking, Boxing and more track and field</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Algerian boxer Imane Khelif’s tumultuous Paris Olympics run culminates Friday with a gold-medal bout, while gold medals will be awarded in track and field, beach volleyball, soccer and breaking as the 2024 Olympics begin to wind down.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/09/what-to-watch-friday-breaking-boxing-and-more-track-and-field/"  >(The Associated Press, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 11 Aug 2024 20:30:42 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 11 Aug 2024 20:30:42 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Nick Robertson, The Hill">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/11/zelensky-warns-of-fire-at-russian-occupied-nuclear-power-plant-radiation-levels-within-norm.webp" alt="Zelensky warns of fire at Russian-occupied nuclear power plant, radiation levels 'within norm'"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Zelensky warns of fire at Russian-occupied nuclear power plant, radiation levels 'within norm'</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky said Sunday that the Russian military had started a fire on the grounds of the Zaporizhzhia Nuclear Power Plant (NPP), warning of potential damage but assuring that radiation levels in the area remain normal.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/11/zelensky-warns-of-fire-at-russian-occupied-nuclear-power-plant-radiation-levels-within-norm/"  >(Nick Robertson, The Hill)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 12 Aug 2024 05:06:44 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 12 Aug 2024 05:06:44 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="WAFAA SHURAFA and SAMY MAGDY, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/12/israel-broadens-its-evacuation-orders-after-deadly-strike-on-gaza-school-turned-shelter.webp" alt="Israel widens evacuation orders in southern Gaza. Hamas wants plans for a deal instead of more talks"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Israel widens evacuation orders in southern Gaza. Hamas wants plans for a deal instead of more talks</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      DEIR AL-BALAH, Gaza Strip (AP) — The Israeli military ordered more evacuations in southern Gaza early Sunday, a day after a deadly airstrike on a school-turned-shelter in the north killed at least 80 Palestinians, according to local health authorities.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/12/israel-broadens-its-evacuation-orders-after-deadly-strike-on-gaza-school-turned-shelter/"  >(WAFAA SHURAFA and SAMY MAGDY, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 12 Aug 2024 06:45:31 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 12 Aug 2024 06:45:31 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="KIM TONG-HYUNG, Associated Press, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/12/south-korea-and-us-will-start-summer-military-drills-next-week-to-counter-north-korean-threats.webp" alt="South Korea and US will start summer military drills next week to counter North Korean threats"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">South Korea and US will start summer military drills next week to counter North Korean threats</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The drills could trigger a belligerent response from North Korea, which portrays them as invasion rehearsals.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/12/south-korea-and-us-will-start-summer-military-drills-next-week-to-counter-north-korean-threats/"  >(KIM TONG-HYUNG, Associated Press, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
