    <h3 itemprop="headline">Jarren Duran suspended 2 games by Red Sox for shouting homophobic slur at fan who heckled him</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Boston Red Sox have suspended Jarren Duran for two games without pay after he shouted a homophobic slur to a fan behind home plate who heckled him in a loss to the Houston Astros.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/12/red-sox-jarren-duran-suspended-2-games-for-shouting-homophobic-slur-at-fan-who-heckled-him/"  >(Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
