    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump won't yet say how he will vote on Florida's abortion amendment</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Former President Donald Trump on Thursday said he won't yet answer a question regarding how he will vote on Florida's amendment that would enshrine abortion rights in the state Constitution.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/08/trump-wont-yet-say-how-he-will-vote-on-floridas-abortion-amendment/"  >(Kevin Accettulla, WFLA, NBC)</a>
