    <h3 itemprop="headline">Fox News Politics: Kamala of Troy</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The latest updates from the 2024 campaign trail, exclusive interviews and more Fox News politics content
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/12/fox-news-politics-kamala-troy/"  >(Fox News)</a>
